        "heading": "Future Tense Formation",
        "content": "Add endings to the FULL infinitive (don't remove -ar/-er/-ir!):\n                              → -án = ellos/Uds.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "spanish": "-é",
            "english": "yo"
          },
          {
