            "spanish": "-á",
            "english": "él/ella/Ud."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "-emos",
            "english": "nosotros"
          },
          {
            "spanish": "-án",
            "english": "ellos/Uds."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "lesson",
        "heading": "Examples: HABLAR",
        "content": "Full infinitive + endings:\n                              \n   ✏️ Exercise: Mañana yo ___ español. (hablar)\n\n   ✏️ Exercise: Ellos ___ a las ocho. (llegar)",
        "examples": [
          {
            "spanish": "hablaré",
            "english": "I will speak"
          },
          {
